ple-new-projects-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/fromsoftware-hiring-for-multiple-new-projects-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/fromsoftware-hiring-for-multiple-new-projects-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/fromsoftware-hiring-for-multiple-new-projects-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/fromsoftware-hiring-for-multiple-new-projects-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>据报道， <a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/fromsoftware">FromSoftware</a>正在为“多个新项目”开展“大规模招聘”计划，并于 12 月开始举办“在线信息发布会”。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/game-reviews/armored-core-6-fires-of-rubicon-review-3486791">《装甲核心 6：卢比孔河之火》评论：这部科幻惊悚片中火花四射</a></strong></li></ul><p>根据该报告的机器翻译<a href="https://jp.ign.com/games/71483/news/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>，IGN Japan</em></a>声称，<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/armored-core"><em>装甲核心</em></a>开发商将在两个月后举办“职业中期招聘在线信息发布会”。</p><p>在这次招聘活动中，出现了来自角色设计、电影学、游戏编程、用户界面艺术家等特定开发学科的空缺职位。这与公共关系、广告、销售和内部 IT 系统角色相结合。 </p><figure id="attachment_3525695" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3525695" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3525695" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/fromsoftware-hiring-for-multiple-new-projects-3.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/fromsoftware-hiring-for-multiple-new-projects-3.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/fromsoftware-hiring-for-multiple-new-projects-3-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/fromsoftware-hiring-for-multiple-new-projects-3-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/fromsoftware-hiring-for-multiple-new-projects-3-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/fromsoftware-hiring-for-multiple-new-projects-3-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/fromsoftware-hiring-for-multiple-new-projects-3-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3525695" class="wp-caption-text"> 《装甲核心 6：卢比孔河之火》图片来源：Bandai Namco</figcaption></figure><p>此外，参与<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/elden-ring"><em>《Elden Ring》</em></a>和<em>《装甲核心 6：卢比孔河之火》</em>工作的人员将协助这些课程中的考生进行指导和内容交付。</p><p>虽然这些课程是免费的，但它们是为那些已经有经验的人量身定制的，这表明 FromSoftware 希望员工无需太多培训即可上手。</p><p> <em>IGN 日本</em>指出，该举措是“为多个新项目招募开发人员”，这可能意味着一款尚未向公众透露的游戏。</p><p>据了解，FromSoftware 正在支持<em>《装甲核心 6：卢比孔之火》</em>的更新，并且<em>《Elden Ring》</em>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/elden-ring-major-expansion-announced-shadow-of-the-erdtree-3405694">《 <em>Shadow Of The Erdtree》</em>扩展包</a>也在开发中。 </p><figure id="attachment_3525697" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3525697" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3525697" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/fromsoftware-hiring-for-multiple-new-projects-2.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/fromsoftware-hiring-for-multiple-new-projects-2.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/fromsoftware-hiring-for-multiple-new-projects-2-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/fromsoftware-hiring-for-multiple-new-projects-2-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/fromsoftware-hiring-for-multiple-new-projects-2-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/fromsoftware-hiring-for-multiple-new-projects-2-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/fromsoftware-hiring-for-multiple-new-projects-2-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3525697" class="wp-caption-text"> 《Elden Ring》图片来源：Bandai Namco</figcaption></figure><p>这些新员工可能会被安排到这些项目中，但导演宫崎英高表示，在 2022 年游戏奖颁奖典礼上，“Lands Between <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/elden-ring-director-has-several-more-things-planned-for-the-game-3364254">”还将推出“更多内容”</a> 。</p><p>其中之一是<em>罗马斗兽场</em>扩展包，然后是<em>埃尔德树之影</em>扩展包，但可以想象，FromSoftware 可以在续集中以<em>《Elden Ring》</em>为基础。</p><p>在其他游戏新闻中， <a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/larian-studios">Larian Studios</a>重申了<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/baldurs-gate-iii"><em>《博德之门 3》</em></a>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/xbox-series-x">Xbox Series X</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/xbox-series-s">Xbox Series S</a>版本将于今年发布：“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/baldurs-gate-3-xbox-news-is-not-coming-from-dudes-with-33k-twitter-followers-says-larian-3523934">这句话已经说过好几次了，但拥有 3.3 万推特粉丝的家伙一直在为了点赞而说废话</a>。”</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/fromsoftware-reveals-massive-recruitment-drive-for-multiple-new-projects-3525658">FromSoftware 的帖子揭示了“多个新项目”的“大规模招聘”活动，</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
