/www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/2023_joerusso_martinscorsese_getty_2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/2023_joerusso_martinscorsese_getty_2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/2023_joerusso_martinscorsese_getty_2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/2023_joerusso_martinscorsese_getty_2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/marvel-cinematic-universe">漫威</a>导演乔·罗素似乎挖苦了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/martin-scorsese">马丁·斯科塞斯</a>的票房成功。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/killers-of-the-flower-moon-review-martin-scorsese-3448518">《花月杀手》评论：马丁·斯科塞斯令人心碎的真实犯罪冷门</a></strong></li></ul><p>有史以来票房第二高的电影<a href="https://www.nme.com/films/avengers-endgame"><em>《复仇者联盟：终局之战</em></a>》的幕后主创在 Instagram 上上传了一段视频，视频中斯科塞斯称呼他的狗为奥斯卡。</p><p>剪辑中，罗素说道：“啊，你看，他养的是雪纳瑞犬，我喜欢雪纳瑞犬，他的名字叫奥斯卡，真的很可爱。”指的是斯科塞斯多年来获得的奥斯卡奖提名以及他凭借 2006 年电影<em>《无间行者》</em>获得的唯一胜利。</p><p>然后，他展示了自己的雪纳瑞狗，他称之为“票房”，这被认为是对他和他的兄弟安东尼·罗素的漫威票房热门电影的明确致敬。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/Cy30Df-vrJd/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4