8.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/the-finals-open-beta-arriving-tomorrow-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/the-finals-open-beta-arriving-tomorrow-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/the-finals-open-beta-arriving-tomorrow-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>配音演员批评<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/embark-studios">Embark Studios</a>在<em><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/the-finals">《总决赛》</a>中使用人工智能来生成声音，“除了少数例外”。</em></p><ul><li><strong>了解更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/gaming-features/best-fps-games-2979649">最佳 FPS 游戏：2023 年您能玩到的最佳射击游戏是什么？</a></strong></li></ul><p><em>总决赛</em>在<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/pc">PC</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/ps5">PS5</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/xbox-series-xs">Xbox Series X|S</a>上进行公开测试直至 11 月 5 日，并<a href="https://www.nme.com/en_au/news/gaming-news/the-finals-beta-so-successful-that-game-started-to-hit-maximum-players-3524896">取得了巨大成功</a>，仅在<a href="https://steamdb.info/app/2076040/charts/">Steam</a>上就达到了 268,000 名玩家的峰值。</p><p>然而，曾在<em><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/gloomwood">《Gloomwood》</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/games/evil-west">《Evil West</a></em> 》、 <em>《Selaco</em> 》等游戏中工作过的配音演员 Gianni Matragrano 认为游戏中的播音员听起来有点奇怪。</p><p>在播音员角色的标注汇编中，他质疑 Embark Studios 是否使用人工智能为这两个人配音。看看下面：</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">所以我猜总决赛将会有人工智能声音……？ <a href="https://t.co/PIAbR43ZrT">pic.twitter.com/PIAbR43ZrT</a></p><p> — Gianni Matragrano (@GetGianni) <a href="https://twitter.com/GetGianni/status/1718213579382407449?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2023 年 10 月 28 日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>然而，在播客<em>Meet The Makers</em>的一<a href="https://open.spotify.com/episode/5ciiOdwOaDP2s15jF8FUgd?si=478e01ac8056414e&amp;nd=1" target="_blank" rel="noopener">集中</a>，音频设计师 Andreas Glad 和 Carl Tamleht 透露，<em>决赛</em>的播音员和参赛者已由人工智能软件配音。</p><p> “所以问题就来了：画外音讲了什么？问题是，我们使用人工智能，但也有一些例外。所有参赛者的声音（如狗叫声）和我们的两位评论员都是人工智能文本转语音，”Andreas 在 7 月说道（来自<a href="https://www.vg247.com/the-finals-uses-ai-voice-acting" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>VG247</em></a> ）。</p><p> “对于我们所说的发声，比如玩家呼吸、跳跃、跳跃，我们在录音室里用这些来录制，比如只是咕噜声。</p><p> “We can&#39;t really get the AI to perform those kinds of tasks yet, and since it&#39;s only excortive [sic] sounds they will mix pretty well with all the AI text to speech voices.” </p><figure id="attachment_3521321" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3521321" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3521321" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/the-finals-open-beta-arriving-tomorrow-3.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/the-finals-open-beta-arriving-tomorrow-3.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/the-finals-open-beta-arriving-tomorrow-3-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/the-finals-open-beta-arriving-tomorrow-3-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/the-finals-open-beta-arriving-tomorrow-3-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/the-finals-open-beta-arriving-tomorrow-3-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/the-finals-open-beta-arriving-tomorrow-3-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3521321" class="wp-caption-text"> &#39;The Finals&#39; Credit: Embark Studios</figcaption></figure><p> This admission, in spite of the explanation that it “gets [the team] far enough in terms of quality”, has not been received well by voice actors and fans of <em>The Finals</em> .</p><p> “What really sticks with me is that they needed to bring in real actors to get the grunting, effort, and breathing sounds because the AI can&#39;t do it,” <a href="https://twitter.com/KitHarrisonVA/status/1718698967918084403" target="_blank" rel="noopener">said</a> Kit Harrison, who has starred in <em><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/dying-light">Dying Light</a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/games/genshin-impact">Genshin Impact</a></em> and <a href="https://www.nme.com/games/smite"><em>Smite</em></a> .</p><p> “It can&#39;t replicate the noise that I make when I stand up from my chair, but it wants to take MY job?! Don&#39;t make me laugh.”</p><p> “The kicker is, it STILL sounds like crap regardless of how &#39;realistic&#39; they think it sounds,” <a href="https://twitter.com/ElsieLovelock/status/1718546503516541081" target="_blank" rel="noopener">replied</a> Elsie Lovelock ( <em>Wargroove, <a href="https://www.nme.com/games/remothered-broken-porcelain">Remothered: Broken Porcelain</a> , Eastshade</em> ) to Matragano&#39;s post to X. </p><figure id="attachment_3521322" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3521322" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3521322" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/the-finals-open-beta-arriving-tomorrow-2.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/the-finals-open-beta-arriving-tomorrow-2.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/the-finals-open-beta-arriving-tomorrow-2-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/the-finals-open-beta-arriving-tomorrow-2-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/the-finals-open-beta-arriving-tomorrow-2-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/the-finals-open-beta-arriving-tomorrow-2-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/the-finals-open-beta-arriving-tomorrow-2-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3521322" class="